The Game will be played by 7-12 player
Each game has 2 Werewolves, 1 Seer, 1 Doctor and the rest villagers.
During the game, some players will be declared "dead". Dead players are not part of the game but they will be able to see the proceedings of the game. When the rules say "players", they mean living players only.The game begins with a night phase. At night, the moderator says, "Werewolves, open your eyes." The players who are werewolves can chat with each other and the werewolves should silently agree on one person.